countries.name: Japan
countries.description: Japan is an island country in East Asia, located in the northwest Pacific Ocean. Known for its traditional arts, including tea ceremonies, calligraphy, and flower arranging, Japan is also famous for its modern innovations, electronics, and beautiful landscapes.

countries.name: France
countries.description: France, known for its art, fashion, and cuisine, is one of the most visited countries in the world. From the Eiffel Tower in Paris to the beaches of the French Riviera, theres a lot to explore.

countries.name: Brazil
countries.description: Brazil is known for its vibrant culture, stunning beaches, and the Amazon rainforest. Its the largest country in South America, famous for Carnival, samba, and its love for football.
